Third-Party Components Notice

This project includes and/or relies on third-party libraries under `libs/`.
These components remain under their respective original licenses and are not
relicensed under this project's MIT terms.

Included third-party components currently used in this addon package include:
- LibThreatClassic2 (`libs/LibThreatClassic2.lua`)
- LibStub (`libs/LibStub/LibStub.lua`)
- CallbackHandler-1.0 (`libs/CallbackHandler-1.0/`)
- Ace3 modules used by LibThreatClassic2:
  - AceAddon-3.0
  - AceComm-3.0
  - AceEvent-3.0
  - AceTimer-3.0
  - AceBucket-3.0
  - AceSerializer-3.0

Please refer to the license files and headers shipped with those libraries
for exact terms and attribution details.

